627" id="mwApw">10.2307/2708627</a>. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./JSTOR" title="JSTOR" id="mwAp0">JSTOR</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwAp4"> </span><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="//www.jstor.org/stable/2708627" id="mwAp8">2708627</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+the+History+of+Ideas&amp;rft.atitle=The+Spread+of+Ibn+Khald%C3%BBn%27s+Ideas+on+Climate+and+Culture&amp;rft.volume=28&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=415-22&amp;rft.date=1967&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F2708627&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F2708627&amp;rft_id=info%3Abibcode%2F1961JHI....22..215C&amp;rft.aulast=Gates&amp;rft.aufirst=Warren+E.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AIbn+Khaldun" class="Z3988" id="mwAqA"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt441" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwAqE"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-57" id="cite_note-57"><a href="./Ibn_Khaldun#cite_ref-57" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-57" class="mw-reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFDhaouadi1990" class="citation journal">Dhaouadi, M. (1 September 1990). "Ibn Khaldun: The Founding Father Of Eastern Sociology". <i id="mwAqI">International Sociology</i>. <b id="mwAqM">5</b> (3): 319–35. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier" id="mwAqQ">doi</a>:<a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.1177%2F026858090005003007" id="mwAqU">10.1177/026858090005003007</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=International+Sociology&amp;rft.atitle=Ibn+Khaldun%3A+The+Founding+Father+Of+Easte