<li id="mwAuU"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20070928013846/http://www.ibnjaldun.com/index.php?L=7" id="mwAuY">Ibn Khaldun. The Mediterranean in the 14th century: Rise and fall of Empires</a>. <i id="mwAuc">Andalusian Legacy</i> exhibition in the <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Alcazar_of_Seville" title="Alcazar of Seville" id="mwAug" class="mw-redirect">Alcazar of Seville</a></li>
<li id="mwAuk"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.tunisiancommunity.org/wordpress/?page_id=834" id="mwAuo">The Ibn Khaldun Community Service Award©</a></li>
<li id="mwAus"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://cliodynamics.ru/index.php?option=com_content&amp;task=view&amp;id=151&amp;Itemid=70" id="mwAuw">Ibn Khaldun meets Al Saud</a></li>
<li id="mwAu0"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.tunisiancommunity.org/wordpress/?page_id=249" id="mwAu4">The Ibn Khaldun Institute</a></li>
