</section><section data-mw-section-id="23" id="mwAvE"><h3 id="Non-English">Non-English</h3>
<ul id="mwAvI"><li id="mwAvM"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://sites.google.com/site/ibnkhaldun21/" id="mwAvQ">Multilingual tunisian academic web site on Ibn Khaldun</a></li>
<li id="mwAvU"><span class="languageicon" about="#mwt216" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"fr icon","href":"./Template:Fr_icon"},"params":{},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAvY">(in French)</span><link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:Articles_with_French-language_external_links" about="#mwt216" id="mwAvc"/> <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120526102936/http://www.at-tawhid.net/article-expose-simplifie-sur-la-theologie-scolastique-al-ilm-ul-kalam-ibn-khaldun-45868741.html" id="mwAvg">Exposé simplifié sur la théologie scolastique</a></li>
<li id="mwAvk"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20040507183818/http://membres.lycos.fr/benikou/" id="mwAvo">Chapters from the Muqaddimah and the History of Ibn Khaldun <b id="mwAvs">in Arabic</b></a></li>
<li id="mwAvw">Ismail Küpeli: <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.grin.com/e-book/70021/ibn-khaldun-und-das-politische-system-syriens-eine-gegenueberstellung" id="mwAv0"><i id="mwAv4">Ibn Khaldun und das politische System Syriens – Eine Gegenüberstellung</i></a>, München, 2007, <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt217" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"978-3-638-75458-3"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAv8"/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" about="#mwt217">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" about="#mwt217"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-3-638-75458-3" title="Special:BookSources/978-3-638-75458-3" about="#mwt217" id="mwAwA">978-3-638-75458-3</a> (German e-book about the politics of Syria with reference to the political theory of Ibn Khaldun)</li>
<li id="mwAwE"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://lomonosov-msu.ru/archive/Lomonosov_2013/2084/25645_8036.pdf" id="mwAwI"><i id="mwAwM">Kuchinov A.M. Ibn Khaldun influence on social thought development</i></a> // Lomonosov-2013. – Moscow, 2013. In Russian.</li>
<li id="mwAwQ"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.teses.usp.br/teses/disponiveis/8/8159/tde-03052018-091006/en.php" id="mwAwU"><i id="mwAwY">Master's thesis on Ibn Khaldun published by FFLCH-USP in 2017</i></a> Roschel, Renato - São Paulo, 2017. In Portuguese.</li></ul>
